      <title>开云集团警告上半年营业利润将因 Gucci 销量下滑而下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/gucci-owner-kering-posts-10-drop-q1-sales-sluggish-chinese-demand-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国奢侈品集团开云集团周二表示，由于富有的消费者限制了其明星品牌古驰 (Gucci) 的产品支出，导致第一季度销售额下降，该集团预计上半年营业利润将下降 40% 至 45%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/gucci-owner-kering-posts-10-drop-q1-sales-sluggish-chinese-demand-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 15:50:28 GMT</pubDate>
