      <title>受中国电动汽车战争期间重组成本影响，日本电产公布季度意外亏损</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nidec-posts-quarterly-loss-hit-by-restructuring-costs-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本电动机制造商日本电产周二公布，由于为应对中国电动汽车市场激烈的价格竞争而采取重组措施的成本，该公司一月至三月季度出现意外运营亏损。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nidec-posts-quarterly-loss-hit-by-restructuring-costs-2024-04-23/</guid>
